    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You can use `_snippetResult` instead after setting up that on your index. https://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/searching/highlighting-snippeting/#snippeting-overview\r\n\r\nBasically make sure that attribute is in `attributesToSnippet`\r\n\r\n```js\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n  instantsearch.widgets.configure({\r\n    attributesToSnippet: ['description:5'], // 5 words, still highlighted\r\n  })\r\n);\r\n```",
